105
00:06:17,043 --> 00:06:19,294
(SIGHS) Oh my God.

106
00:06:19,295 --> 00:06:23,883
Oh my God. (SIGHS)
That scared the shit out of me.

107
00:06:26,427 --> 00:06:28,637
