and I think I've placed it.

160
00:11:02,620 --> 00:11:04,497
- VICTORIA: Mmm.
- Do you know Claire Popovich?

161
00:11:05,206 --> 00:11:06,956
Mmm. Yes. I do.

162
00:11:06,957 --> 00:11:08,083
You and I

163
