169
00:11:28,729 --> 00:11:32,316
Yeah, your hair, your...
your hair was different, right?

170
00:11:33,818 --> 00:11:35,902
Well, maybe, maybe. Maybe.

171
00:11:35,903 --> 00:11:38,279
Um, these are my friends.

172
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:39,823
