173
00:11:39,824 --> 00:11:41,991
- Hi.
- Hey. What's up?

174
00:11:41,992 --> 00:11:44,369
Gosh, it's such
a small world, isn't it?

175
00:11:44,370 --> 00:11:45,496
(VICTORIA CHUCKLES)

176
00:11:49,166 --> 00:11:51,961
I just saw Claire
right before I left.

177
00:11:53,129 --> 00:11:55,255
If I talk to her,
I'll tell her you said hello.

178
00:11:55,256 --> 00:11:58,592
