206
00:13:31,519 --> 00:13:34,355
(SAXON LAUGHING)

207
00:13:39,193 --> 00:13:41,778
- Sawatdee kha.
- Hey, Mook!

208
00:13:41,779 --> 00:13:43,780
I just want
to confirm this morning

209
00:13:43,781 --> 00:13:46,616
